<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gamla tak ah huihpi leh guohpi,
 Khel lam akhun;
 Kumsawt nawpna vak chuh a vak hi,
 Sun bang vak zing gamah.

[V2]
 Ziechun lungkham nat leh kikhen,
 Na um ta puona;
 Luigal achun kituok khawm hitiu,
 Bittak in van In ah.

[V3]
 2. Gamla tak tui kinawk khel gam khu,
 Ginnan ka zuon;
 Hehpih na'n khawpi hawih chu ei hilh,
 Tun ding ka kinem hi.

[V4]
 3. Gamla tak luiguom gal hehpihte,
 A kai tau hi;
 &quot;Umna tamtak&quot; umna mun achun,
 Kituok khawm vek tai tiu.

[V5]
 4. Nunnawp, kipahna zingkhuo a vak,
 Aw, ni lopi;
 Ziechun lungkham na mitthi luong cheng,
 Isu'n thiek-hul ta'n a.</lyrics>
<title>THE HOME LAND SHORE</title>
<hymn_number>383</hymn_number>
</song>